				<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a></div>				<h1>Putting Together a Budget DIY Lighting System</h1>				<div class="tabs"></div>
												<!-- begin content --><div class="node">
        <span class="submitted">Submitted by Adrian Broughton on Sat, 2006-03-25 08:00.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><a href="/content/articles" rel="tag" title="">Articles</a> | <a href="/topics/equipment" rel="tag" title="">Equipment</a> | <a href="/topics/equipment/flash_lighting" rel="tag" title="">Flash/Lighting</a></span>
    <div class="content"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->
<p><b>Adrian Broughton, 25 March 2006</b></p>
<div class="box">
<b>Article Sections:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#introduction" name="top">Introduction</a></li>
<li><a href="#gettingstarted">Getting Started</a></li>
<li><a href="#components">Components</a></li>
